- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language and its syntactic complexity. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories as the paper uses computational simulations to study the language evolution mechanism. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are less likely categories but still possible as the paper discusses the structural properties of language and its evolution.
